      %h2 Beliefs
      .item
        %h3 Senses / Boarderless
        .description
          IT skills age so fast. Acquiring "senses", not only skills, enables to adapt to any environment, and to find better solution without boarder.
      .item
        %h3 Technology as both "Hack" and "Solution"
